social_posts.post_text: Definitely over a month late on posting some of my favorite memories from January in Florida but hey better late than never/mom life, am I right?! Giving this a permanent spot because I never want to forget these special memories 🫶🏼🌴

Currently in my skin care era and loving it 💁🏼‍♀️ I recently got a Platinum Hydrafacial courtesy of @bossgalbeautybar and it was beyond amazing! This is my new favorite facial - it cleanses, exfoliates, extracts, and hydrates your skin. It also includes dermaplane, lymphatic drainage, and a hydrojelly mask with LED light therapy to reduce visible signs of aging….YES PLEASE. The post-hydrafacial glow is real!!
AND @bossgalbeautybar gave me a code for you to use when you book any facial! Use XOLAUREN to get a free dermaplane (my fav) with your service!
Switzerland, we 🤍 you (part 1)
A few favorite Switzerland memories (part 2), this time from sunny and absolutely beautiful St. Moritz 🌞 Such a special place. Truly breathtaking!
Switzerland love (part 3) in Scuol 🤍 Quiet, peaceful, wild, and breathtakingly stunning. I could go on and on about Switzerland. The mountains, fresh air, people, pace of life. We love it all 🤍
A little bit of yummy food, a little bit of random…and lots of fun. SUMMER ☀️

I had Radio Frequency Microneedling done a few weeks ago at @bossgalbeautybar and WOOWWWW did I love it! It’s different than traditional microneedling because in addition to creating microscopic channels that stimulate the natural production of collagen, it delivers radio-frequency heat energy to promote collagen and elastin that tightens and lifts the skin! The best part about RF microneedling is the short downtime. My post-treatment redness went WAY down so quickly which was amazing! All in all, it was such a great experience and my skin feels sooo good! Don’t forget to use my code XOLAUREN for a FREE dermaplane with any treatment! 🤍
Little snippets of some favorite moments from our quick Miami getaway last week to celebrate our 10 year anni a few weeks early! 🤍 Mostly featuring lots of pool time and lots of good food 🫶🏼

10 years of marriage, our sweet boy starting kindergarten tomorrow, and a little girl who gives the best hugs and makes us laugh every day…time flies when you are having fun! Happy anniversary, my love 🤍🥂

This month for my partnership with @bossgalbeautybar, I did something I haven’t tried before: lasers! I was so excited to try the BBL + Moxi laser combo to help with underlying redness in my face and sun damage spots. The whole process was great! The wonderful @laura_bossgal_np did my treatment, and walked me through the whole process, step by step 🤍
I love that there was minimal downtime and I really love my results! My skin feels super smooth and the reduction of redness on my face is definitely noticeable. Don’t forget to use my code “Lauren643B” to get $20 off your first @bossgalbeautybar treatment!

Video snippets of Paris and London that make me want to go back asap! Traveling isn’t always smooth or fun 100% of the time, but it is SO rewarding and worth it. Such special memories that I will always cherish!
High tea at @mo_hydepark & seeing his second @spursofficial football (soccer) match were Rhys’ favorite activities in London on our recent trip….and I have to say, I agree!

Hi friends! This month at @bossgalbeautybar I did the limited time, limited edition Icy Hot Facial and it was SO GOOD. Now that winter is here, my skin has needed a refresh and this did *just* the trick!
This amazing facial:
✨Helps improve the appearance of your skin by inducing anti-inflammatory responses and the release of endorphins
✨Helps reduce redness and inflammation 
✨Promotes pore tightening and collagen stimulation 
✨Uses a hot & cold hammer device which felt SO good 
✨Finishes with one of their amazing hydro jelly masks! 

I added dermaplane and the Celluma LED light which are my favorite services to add to any facial! 

Don’t forget, if you are new to @bossgalbeautybar, use my code Lauren643B for $20 off any treatment! #bossgalbeautybar #partner
